message.body: Can I treat you to dinner tonight? For the boxes and cat sitting and painting.
You can get a meat stick at Choy Wong or a meat steak at Outback Steakhouse pizzeria.
Still working . Won't be home for a while. I would get Choy Wong I guess
Cool. I will order and pick up and bring to you just let me know what you want when you will be home.
I want large beef with broccoli no rice, very little brown sauce. Be home before 7
Cool. I'll order at 6:45 and head over around 7. See you soon.
Hey if u bring your computer we can watch a movie downstairs
Okay I will bring it. Yeah meet me! It might be okay but just in case. I'm leaving now.
Also I can meet u at Choy rhombus if you can't carry it
